<https://github.com/anntanp/mocho-odk/mocho/mocho-full.owl> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://github.com/anntanp/mocho-odk/mocho/mocho-full.owl> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionIRI> <https://github.com/anntanp/mocho-odk/mocho/releases/2026-03-11/mocho-full.owl> .
<https://github.com/anntanp/mocho-odk/mocho/mocho-full.owl> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "A middle ontology bridging the Europeana Data Model (EDM) as top-level ontology with domain ontologies: RDA, Records in Contexts Ontology (RiC-O), Music Ontology, Audio Commons Ontology (ACO), and CIDOC CRM via LRMoo/FRBRoo. The WEMI model (Work, Expression, Manifestation, Item) serves as the central conceptual framework, with RDA entity classes as the canonical middle-layer.\n" .
<https://github.com/anntanp/mocho-odk/mocho/mocho-full.owl> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/deed.en> .
<https://github.com/anntanp/mocho-odk/mocho/mocho-full.owl> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Middle Ontology for Cultural Heritage Objects (MOCHO)"@en .
<https://github.com/anntanp/mocho-odk/mocho/mocho-full.owl> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "2026-03-11" .
