<http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/description> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Une description d'un actif."@fr .
<http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/description> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Description may include but is not limited to: an abstract, a table of contents, a graphical representation, or a free-text account of the resource."@en .
<http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/description> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Beschreibung"@de .
