<http://purl.org/vocab/frbr/core#abridgementOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "It identifies the entire expression of an abridged one."@en .
<http://purl.org/vocab/frbr/core#abridgementOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is abridgement of"@en .
