<http://purl.org/vocab/frbr/core#producerOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The producer of a particular manifestation."@en .
<http://purl.org/vocab/frbr/core#producerOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is producer of"@en .
# 
