<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/rdfs/cidoc-crm#P129_is_about> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/rdfs/cidoc-crm#P129_is_about> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "crm:P129_is_about"@en .
