<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hadPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadPart> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hadPart> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasPartOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hadPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hadPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hadPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a Thing to a Thing that was a constitutive or component\n         part of that Thing in the past."@en .
