<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasComponentTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isComponentOfTransitive> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasComponentTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasComponentTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasComponentTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasComponentTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects an Instantiation to another Instantiation that is,\n         directly or indirectly, a component of that Instantiation. This is a transitive\n         relation."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasComponentTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a pour composant transitif"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasComponentTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has component transitive"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasComponentTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene como componente transitivo"@es .
# 
