<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasCopy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesInTime> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasCopy> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isCopyOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasCopy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasCopy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasCopy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a Record Resource to a copy of that Record\n         Resource."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasCopy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a pour copie"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasCopy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has copy"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasCopy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene como copia"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasCopy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Is both a temporal and genetic relation between the two Record\n         Resources."@en .
# 
