<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectComponentOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects an Instantiation to another Instantiation that is its\n         direct component."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a directement pour composant"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has direct component"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene directamente como componente"@es .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectPart
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasPartTransitive> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectPart> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectPartOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a Thing to a Thing that is a direct constitutive or\n         component part of that Thing."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a directement pour partie"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has direct part"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene directamente como parte"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasDirectPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "To be used only when the current partitive relation is direct,\n         without any intermediate node between the related things."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasGeneticLinkToRecordResource
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasGeneticLinkToRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasGeneticLinkToRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasGeneticLinkToRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasGeneticLinkToRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasGeneticLinkToRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasGeneticLinkToRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects two Record Resources when there is a genetic link between\n         them. Genetic in this sense is as defined by diplomatics, i.e. the process by which a\n         Record Resource is developed. This relation is symmetric."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasGeneticLinkToRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a une relation génétique avec la ressource\n         archivistique"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasGeneticLinkToRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has genetic link to record resource"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasGeneticLinkToRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene vínculo de origen con recurso documental"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasGeneticLinkToRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Use to connect two Record Resources only if it is not possible\n         to use a narrower, more specific, asymmetric Record Resource to Record Resource relation,\n         for example is original of."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadAnalogueInstantiation
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadAnalogueInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadAnalogueInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadInstantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadAnalogueInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasAnalogueInstantiationOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadAnalogueInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadAnalogueInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadAnalogueInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a record resource to one of its analogue instantiations,\n         whether it exists or has been lost or destroyed."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadAnalogueInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a ou a eu pour instanciation analogique"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadAnalogueInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has or had analogue instantiation"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadAnalogueInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene o tenía como instanciación analogica"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadAnalogueInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "In some situations, it may be useful or necessary to connect a\n         record resource to an analogue instantiation that no longer exists or has been\n         lost."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadComponent
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadComponent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadPart> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasComponentOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects an Instantiation to one of its present or past component\n         instantiations."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a ou a eu pour composant"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has or had component"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene o tenía como componente"@es .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDerivedInstantiation
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDerivedInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDerivedInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDerivedInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesInTime> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDerivedInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDerivedFromInstantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDerivedInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDerivedInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDerivedInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects an instantiation to an instantiation that is derived from\n         it, whether it exists or has been lost or destroyed."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDerivedInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a ou a eu pour instanciation dérivée"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDerivedInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has or had derived instantiation"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDerivedInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene o tenía como instanciación derivada"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDerivedInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "In some situations, it may be useful or necessary to connect an\n         instantiation to an instantiation that was derived from it but no longer exists or or has\n         been lost."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDigitalInstantiation
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDigitalInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDigitalInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadInstantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDigitalInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDigitalInstantiationOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDigitalInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDigitalInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDigitalInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a record resource to one of its digital instantiations,\n         whether it exists or has been lost or destroyed."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDigitalInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a ou a eu pour instanciation numérique"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDigitalInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has or had digital instantiation"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDigitalInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene o tenía como instanciación digital"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDigitalInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "This property can be used, among other cases, when you want to\n         convert findings aids encoded in EAD/XML and need a simple and accurate migration path to\n         process dao or daogrp EAD elements. Also, in some situations, it may be useful or necessary\n         to connect a record resource to a digital instantiation that no longer exists or or has\n         been lost."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadInstantiation
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasInstantiationOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a Record Resource to an Instantiation, which either may\n         exist or may have been lost or destroyed."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a ou a eu pour instanciation"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has or had instantiation"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene o tenía como instanciación"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "In some situations, it may be useful or necessary to connect a\n         record resource to an instantiation that no longer exists or or has been lost, when some of\n         its characteristics are known from some source, like an old finding aid."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadPart
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadPart> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasPartOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a Thing to a constitutive or component part of that\n         Thing."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a ou a eu pour partie"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has or had part"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene o tenía como parte"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Use to connect a Thing to another Thing that is or was a part of\n         the whole Thing only if it is not possible to use a narrower, more specific whole/part\n         relation, for example has or had constituent. The end of existence of a whole/part relation\n         may affect the integrity or nature of the domain entity."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasPartTransitive
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasPartTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasPartTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadPart> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasPartTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isPartOfTransitive> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasPartTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasPartTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasPartTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasPartTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a Thing to a Thing that is, directly or indirectly, a\n         constitutive or component part of that Thing. This is a transitive relation."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasPartTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a pour partie transitif"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasPartTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has part transitive"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasPartTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene como parte transitivo"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasPartTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "To be used, either to infer, then query or browse, relations\n         from existing direct 'hasDirectPart' relations between things, or to record a current\n         partitive relation when you do not know if there are intermediate nodes between the related\n         things."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasReply
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasReply> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasReply> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasReply> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesInTime> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasReply> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isReplyTo> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasReply> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasReply> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasReply> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a Record Resource to a reply, usually in the form of\n         correspondence."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasReply> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a pour réponse"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasReply> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has reply"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasReply> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene como contestación"@es .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isComponentOfTransitive
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isComponentOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isComponentOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasComponentOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isComponentOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isPartOfTransitive> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isComponentOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isComponentOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isComponentOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isComponentOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects an Instantiation to another Instantiation of which it is,\n         directly or indirectly, a component. This is a transitive relation."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isComponentOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "es componente de transitivo"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isComponentOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est un composant de transitif"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isComponentOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is component of transitive"@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isCopyOf
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isCopyOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isCopyOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#followsInTime> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isCopyOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasGeneticLinkToRecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isCopyOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isCopyOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isCopyOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of 'has copy' object property."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isCopyOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "es copia de"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isCopyOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est la copie de"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isCopyOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is copy of"@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectComponentOf
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isComponentOfTransitive> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectPartOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects an Instantiation to another Instantiation of which it is\n         a direct component."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "es componente directo de"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est le composant direct de"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is direct component of"@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectPartOf
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isPartOfTransitive> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a Thing to a Thing of which it is direct constitutive or\n         component part."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "es parte directa de"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "fait directement partie de"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is direct part of"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "To be used only when the current partitive relation is direct,\n         without any intermediate node between the related things."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isEquivalentTo
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects two Things that are considered equivalent."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "equivale a"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est l’équivalent de"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is equivalent to"@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isFunctionallyEquivalentTo
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isFunctionallyEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isFunctionallyEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isEquivalentTo> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isFunctionallyEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isFunctionallyEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isFunctionallyEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isFunctionallyEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isFunctionallyEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects two Instantiations which may be considered as equivalent.\n         This relation is symmetric."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isFunctionallyEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "equivale funcionalmente a"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isFunctionallyEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est fonctionnellement équivalente à"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isFunctionallyEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is functionally equivalent to"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isFunctionallyEquivalentTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Two Instantiations, from some point of view, may be considered\n         as equivalent. This equivalence is usually based upon the fact that the Instantiations have\n         at least the same intellectual content (they instantiate the same Record\n         Resource)."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects two Instantiations. This relation is\n         symmetric."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est associée à l’instanciation"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is instantiation associated with instantiation"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "se asocia con la instanciación"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Use only if it is not possible to specify a narrower\n         Instantiation to Instantiation relation, for example is functionally equivalent\n         to."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasAnalogueInstantiationOf
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasAnalogueInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasAnalogueInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasInstantiationOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasAnalogueInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasAnalogueInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasAnalogueInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of 'has or had analogue instantiation' object\n         property."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasAnalogueInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "es or era instanciación analogica de"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasAnalogueInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est ou a été une instanciation analogique de"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasAnalogueInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is or was analogue instantiation of"@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasComponentOf
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasPartOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of 'has or had component' object property."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "es o era componente de"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est ou a été un composant de"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is or was component of"@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDerivedFromInstantiation
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDerivedFromInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDerivedFromInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#followsInTime> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDerivedFromInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isInstantiationAssociatedWithInstantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDerivedFromInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDerivedFromInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDerivedFromInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of 'has or had derived instantiation' object\n         property."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDerivedFromInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "es o era un derivado de instanciación"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDerivedFromInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est ou a été une instanciation dérivée de"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDerivedFromInstantiation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is or was derived from instantiation"@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDigitalInstantiationOf
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDigitalInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDigitalInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasInstantiationOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDigitalInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDigitalInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDigitalInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of 'has or had digital instantiation' object\n         property."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDigitalInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "es o era instanciación digital de"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDigitalInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est ou a été une instanciation numérique de"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDigitalInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is or was digital instantiation of"@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasInstantiationOf
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of 'has or had instantiation' object\n         property."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "es o era instanciación de"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est ou a été une instanciation de"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasInstantiationOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is or was instantiation of"@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasPartOf
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of 'has or had part' relation."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "es o era parte de"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est ou a été une partie de"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is or was part of"@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isPartOfTransitive
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isPartOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isPartOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasPartOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isPartOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isPartOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isPartOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isPartOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a Thing to a Thing of which it is a a constitutive or\n         component part, directly or indirectly. This is a transitive relation."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isPartOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "es parte de transitivo"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isPartOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est une partie de transitif"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isPartOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is part of transitive"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isPartOfTransitive> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "To be used, either to infer, then query or browse, relations\n         from existing direct 'isDirectPartOf' relations between things, or to record a current\n         partitive relation when you do not know if there are intermediate nodes between the related\n         things."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects two Record Resources. This relation is\n         symmetric."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "es recurso documental asociado con"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est une ressource archivistique associée avec la ressource\n         archivistique"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is record resource associated with record resource"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Use to connect two Record Resources only if it is not possible\n         to use a narrower, more specific relation, for example has genetic link\n         to."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The most generic relation, is related to, connects any Thing to\n         any other Thing. This relation is symmetric."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est relié à"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "está relacionado con"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is related to"@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isReplyTo
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isReplyTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isReplyTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#followsInTime> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isReplyTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isReplyTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isReplyTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isReplyTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of 'has reply' object property."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isReplyTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "es contestación de"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isReplyTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est une réponse à"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isReplyTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is reply to"@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isSourceOfInformationOfRecordResource
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isSourceOfInformationOfRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isSourceOfInformationOfRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isSourceOfInformationOfRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#recordResourceHasSourceOfInformation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isSourceOfInformationOfRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isSourceOfInformationOfRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isSourceOfInformationOfRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a Record Resource to a Record Resource, when the first is\n         used as a source of information for producing the content of the second one."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isSourceOfInformationOfRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "es fuente de información de recurso documental"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isSourceOfInformationOfRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est une source d’information de la ressource\n         archivistique"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isSourceOfInformationOfRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is source of information of Record Resource"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isSourceOfInformationOfRecordResource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Can be used, for example, for a Record Resource used to produce\n         a Record having documentary form type Authority Record or Finding Aid. Not to be confused\n         with the 'hasGeneticLinkToRecordResource' object property."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedFrom
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasDerivedFromInstantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedInto> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of 'migrated into' object property."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a été produite par migration de"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "migrado desde"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "migrated from"@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedInto
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedInto> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedInto> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadDerivedInstantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedInto> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedInto> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedInto> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects an Instantiation to a version it has been migrated\n         into."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedInto> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a été migrée vers"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedInto> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "migrado a"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedInto> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "migrated into"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#migratedInto> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Use for digital instantiations."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesInTime
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesInTime> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesInTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesOrPreceded> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesInTime> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesInTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesInTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesInTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a Thing to a Thing that follows it in chronological\n         order. This is a transitive relation."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesInTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "precede en el tiempo a"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesInTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "precedes in time"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesInTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "précède dans le temps"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesInTime> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "There may actually be zero to many intermediate Entities,\n         ignored or unknown, in the chronological sequence between the two connected\n         Entities."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesOrPreceded
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesOrPreceded> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesOrPreceded> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRelatedTo> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesOrPreceded> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesOrPreceded> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesOrPreceded> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a Thing to a Thing that follows or followed it in some\n         sequence."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesOrPreceded> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "precede o precedía secuencialmente a"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesOrPreceded> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "precedes or preceded"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesOrPreceded> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "précède ou a précédé"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#precedesOrPreceded> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "The relation does not specify by itself what criteria are used\n         for ordering the sequence. There may actually be zero to many intermediate Entities,\n         ignored or unkown, in the sequence between the two connected Things. Can be used, for\n         example, for specifying that some Record 'precedes' (has next) some Record within a Record\n         Set."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#recordResourceHasSourceOfInformation
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#recordResourceHasSourceOfInformation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#recordResourceHasSourceOfInformation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isRecordResourceAssociatedWithRecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#recordResourceHasSourceOfInformation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#recordResourceHasSourceOfInformation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordResource> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#recordResourceHasSourceOfInformation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a Record Resource to a Record Resource, when the second\n         one is used as a source of information for producing the content of the first\n         one."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#recordResourceHasSourceOfInformation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Record Resource has source of information"@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#recordResourceHasSourceOfInformation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est une ressource archivistique qui a pour source\n         d’information"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#recordResourceHasSourceOfInformation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "recurso documental tiene como fuente de información"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#recordResourceHasSourceOfInformation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Can be used, for example, to connect a Record that has\n         documentary form type Authority Record or Finding Aid, and a Record Resource used as a\n         source of information for it. Not to be confused with the 'hasGeneticLinkToRecordResource'\n         object property."@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasComponentOf
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasComponentOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasPartOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Instantiation> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects an Instantiation to another Instantiation of which it was\n         a component in the past."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a été le composant de"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "era componente de"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasComponentOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "was component of"@en .
# 
# https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasPartOf
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isOrWasPartOf> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Thing> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a Thing to a Thing of which it was a constitutive or\n         component part in the past."@en .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "a fait partie de"@fr .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "era parte de"@es .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#wasPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "was part of"@en .
