# 
# http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement
<http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "dcterms:ProvenanceStatement"@en .
<http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Any changes in ownership and custody of a resource since its creation that are significant for its authenticity, integrity, and interpretation."@en .
