# 
# http://purl.org/ontology/mo/AnalogSignal
<http://purl.org/ontology/mo/AnalogSignal> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
