<http://purl.org/spar/fabio/Manifestation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A subclass of FRBR manifestation, restricted to manifestations of fabio:Expressions. fabio:Manifestation specifically applies to electronic (digital) as well as to physical manifestations of expressions.  \n\nExamples of different manifestations of a single 'version of record' expression of a scholarly work include an article in a print journal or the on-line version of that article as a web page."@en .
<http://purl.org/spar/fabio/Manifestation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "fabio:Manifestation"@en .
# 
