<http://purl.org/spar/fabio/SubjectTerm> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A concept that defines a term within the controlled vocabulary of a particular classification system, such as the ACM Computing Classification System or MeSH, the Medical Subject Headings, used as an annotation to describe the subject, meaning or content of an entity."@en .
<http://purl.org/spar/fabio/SubjectTerm> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "fabio:SubjectTerm"@en .
