<http://purl.org/vocab/frbr/core#Endeavour> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "It describes different aspects of user interests in the products of intellectual or artistic artifact."@en .
<http://purl.org/vocab/frbr/core#Endeavour> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "frbr:Endeavour"@en .
