<http://purl.org/vocab/frbr/core#Work> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.org/vocab/frbr/core#Endeavour> .
<http://purl.org/vocab/frbr/core#Work> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/rdfs/cidoc-crm#E89_Propositional_Object> .
<http://purl.org/vocab/frbr/core#Work> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.europeana.eu/schemas/edm/InformationResource> .
