<http://rdaregistry.info/Elements/c/C10001> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://rdaregistry.info/Elements/c/C10001> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://rdaregistry.info/Elements/c/C10013> .
