# http://www.europeana.eu/schemas/edm/EuropeanaObject
<http://www.europeana.eu/schemas/edm/EuropeanaObject> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
