<http://www.europeana.eu/schemas/edm/EuropeanaObject> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "An annotation created by a user through the Europeana portal"@en .
<http://www.europeana.eu/schemas/edm/EuropeanaObject> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Any content created by the users through the service made available by Europeana for that purpose"@en .
<http://www.europeana.eu/schemas/edm/EuropeanaObject> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Any instance of the class EuropeanaAggregation"@en .
