<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioCollection> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A collection of audio manifestations (e.g., a sound pack, an album, a result set of a search over a repository of audio content). As an audio collection is an audio manifestation too, collections may be nested. An audio collection is composed of nodes.\n" .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioCollection> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco> .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioCollection> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Audio collection" .
