<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioExpression> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.org/vocab/frbr/core#Expression> .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioExpression> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The specific intellectual or artistic form that a work takes each time it is \t“realized”, in the audio domain (e.g., the recording or synthesis of music or sounds).\n" .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioExpression> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco> .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioExpression> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "aco:AudioExpression"@en .
