# https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioFile
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioFile> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioFile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.ebu.ch/metadata/ontologies/ebucoreplus#MediaResource> .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioFile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioItem> .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioFile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A concrete audio file (encoded in some format)" .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioFile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco> .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioFile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "aco:AudioFile"@en .
