# https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioItem
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioItem> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioItem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.org/vocab/frbr/core#Item> .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioItem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A concrete exemplar of an audio manifestation (e.g., a copy of a CD or a specific media file).\n" .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioItem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco> .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioItem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "aco:AudioItem"@en .
