# https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioManifestation
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioManifestation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioManifestation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.org/vocab/frbr/core#Manifestation> .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioManifestation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The physical embodiment of an audio expression (e.g., a musical track, a sound, an album).\n" .
