<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#DigitalSignal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#Signal> .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#DigitalSignal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A digital signal." .
