<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#Signal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#AudioExpression> .
<https://w3id.org/ac-ontology/aco#Signal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A subclass of AudioExpression, representing a signal, for example a master signal produced by a performance and a recording.\n" .
