<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Type> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Concept> .
<https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Type> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A superclass for any type of some thing. A type characterizes an\n         entity."@en .
